      Reworked with an extended heel geometry, pillowed tongue and softer, lighter foams, the HOKA Bondi 8 men's road-running shoes take a bold step forward to a distinctly different ride.

      Features

      • Rear crash pad has a billowed effect that affords a soft and balanced ride from heel strike to forefoot transition
      • All-new lightweight, resilient foam offers superior cushioning that's the perfect blend of soft and bouncy
      • Partially gusseted tongue is pillowed for extra comfort
      • Recycled Ortholite Hybrid sockliners
      • Zonal rubber placement keeps shoe weight low
      • Heel pull tab for easy on/off
